Running the Benerator scripts
=============================

1. Download databene benerator: http://sourceforge.net/projects/benerator/
2. Extract it somewhere.
3. Set BENERATOR_HOME environment variable to point to the extracted directory:
	
	export BENERATOR_HOME=/Users/david.keen/databene-benerator-0.6.2

4. Make the scripts executable:

	chmod a+x $BENERATOR+HOME/bin/*.sh
	
5. Ensure JAVA_HOME is set.
6. Set BENERATOR_OPTS environment variable to define the stage and database
   Stage may be one of [development|medium|large]:

	export BENERATOR_OPTS="-Dstage=development -Ddatabase=mysql"
   
6. Run the script

	$BENERATOR_HOME/bin/benerator.sh amee.ben.xml
	

